These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, cherry, apple, cranberry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, classical, jazz, r&b
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, indian, british, nigerian
4 different pets are kept: mouse, cat, dog, rabbit
 1. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 2. the person eating pumpkin is in an even position##4
 3. the egyptian is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
 4. the british is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 5. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
 7. the indian is the person eating apple##1
 8. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the rabbit and the fan of r&b##2
10. the person eating pumpkin is the owner of the rabbit##1
11. the fan of jazz is the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | apple  | pumpkin    | cranberry    | cherry   |
| Music-Genre   | classical     | dubstep   | jazz       | r&b    |
| Nationality   | indian | egyptian | nigerian    | british |
| Pet           | cat | rabbit       | mouse | dog     |

