.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, radish, garlic, zucchini
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, photography, singing, reading
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, japanese, american, malaysian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, snowboarding, rugby, skiing
 1. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
 2. the japanese is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 4. the person eating radish is the canadian##1
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 6. the canadian is on the left or right of the american##3
 7. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 8. the malaysian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 9. the american is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating garlic is in an odd position##4
11. the american is the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | spinach  | radish    | garlic     | zucchini       |
| Hobby         | singing | reading | traveling   | photography |
| Nationality   | american | canadian   | japanese   | malaysian    |
| Sport         | rugby | skiing  | cricket | snowboarding   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up, milk, cola
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, journalist, police-officer, software-developer
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, brazilian, spanish, canadian
4 different pets are kept: ferret, pony, chinchilla, hamster
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the teacher##3
 2. the brazilian is the police-officer##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 4. the teacher is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is the software-developer##1
 6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 7. the owner of the ferret is the canadian##1
 8. the software-developer is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking milk is on the left of the russian##1
10. the owner of the ferret is the person drinking milk##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | milk   | cola    | 7up      |
| Job           | police-officer | teacher | journalist | software-developer     |
| Nationality   | brazilian      | canadian   | russian   | spanish |
| Pet           | hamster         | ferret       | chinchilla  | pony       |

