.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice, cola, tea
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, kiwi, apple, cauliflower
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, puzzles, hiking, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, rugby, sailing, golf
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person eating raspberry##1
 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
 4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking juice is the person who's sport is golf##1
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
 9. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
10. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
11. the person drinking cola is the person eating cauliflower##1
12. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | tea       | cola   | mirinda   | juice   |
| Food       | kiwi        | cauliflower | raspberry    | apple       |
| Hobby      | filmmaking | puzzles    | hiking  | cooking |
| Sport      | rugby  | sailing  | soccer | golf    |

