.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, kale, cherry, cauliflower
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, photography, filmmaking, singing
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, dressmaker, designer, fisherman
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, swimming, tennis, basketball
 1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person eating cauliflower##2
 3. the designer is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the dressmaker is the person eating cranberry##1
 5. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating kale is the entrepreneur##1
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the dressmaker##1
 9. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
10. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
11. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3
12. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | cherry    | cauliflower      | cranberry          | kale    |
| Hobby   | photography | singing       | filmmaking | board-games |
| Job     | fisherman     | designer      | dressmaker     | entrepreneur |
| Sport   | swimming   | basketball | tennis        | cycling   |

