.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee, water, sprite
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, plum, cherry, tomato
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, blues, metal, house
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, thai, egyptian, mexican
 1. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 3. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 4. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 5. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of house is between the egyptian and the fan of blues##2
 7. the fan of metal is the person eating cherry##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is the person eating cherry##1
 9. the thai is on the far right##1
10. the russian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | water  | coffee    | mirinda       | sprite       |
| Food          | tomato    | cherry | plum | broccoli     |
| Music-Genre   | pop | metal        | house    | blues   |
| Nationality   | russian  | egyptian      | mexican    | thai |

