4 different pets are kept: turtle, dog, snake, goldfish
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, airplane, bus, roller
 1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 2. the polish is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 4. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the chinese##3
 5. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 6. the spanish is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 7. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 8. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
 9. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
10. the british is on the far right##1
11. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
12. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | thriller    | epic  | time-travel      |
| Nationality   | chinese      | spanish | polish | british   |
| Pet           | snake       | goldfish | turtle   | dog       |
| Transport     | roller      | bus | jet-ski  | airplane |

