The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, disaster, thriller, time-travel
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, egyptian, french, chinese
4 different pets are kept: pony, lizard, guinea-pig, mouse
 1. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the pony is between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
 3. the russian is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the chinese is on the right of the french##1
 6. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the egyptian##1
 9. the owner of the pony is between the russian and the person watching disaster movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
11. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
12. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing  | sudoku    | camping    | writing |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller   | animation       | disaster  | time-travel    |
| Nationality   | russian | egyptian | french | chinese   |
| Pet           | guinea-pig    | pony        | mouse   | lizard    |

