.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, lime, peach, lettuce
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, spy, adventure, comedy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, country, r&b, disco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, cricket, cycling, surfing
 1. the person eating lime is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 2. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the person watching spy movies and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 5. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
 6. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 7. the fan of disco is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is the person watching spy movies##1
 9. the person eating cranberry is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
11. the person eating cranberry is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of country is on the left of the person eating peach##1
13. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Food          | cranberry     | peach      | lettuce  | lime        |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | adventure | zombie | comedy      |
| Music-Genre   | country      | dubstep        | disco        | r&b        |
| Sport         | surfing | rugby    | cricket      | cycling |

