 1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
 2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 3. the journalist is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is tennis##2
 4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the spanish##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the argentine is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
 8. the spanish is on the right of the argentine##1
 9. the firefighter is on the left of the journalist##1
10. the videographer is in an even position##4
11. the italian is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |       3        |       4       |
