 3. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the social-worker##2
 5. the person eating avocado is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 6. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an odd position##4
 7. the person eating potato is on the far left or far right##3
