 9. the person eating eggplant is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
11. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left or far right##3
12. the paramedic is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
13. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3

