 1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 4. the person watching family movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
10. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | fanta       | tea | cola        | water        |
| Hobby         | board-games | woodworking       | rock-climbing | gardening |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller     | family        | martial-arts    | romance      |
| Sport         | handball     | rowing    | parkour | baseball   |

