.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, d&b, country, r&b
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, indian, malaysian, brazilian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, basketball, biathlon, skiing
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, airplane, roller, trike
 1. the fan of r&b is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the mexican and the brazilian##2
 3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
 4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the indian##1
 5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 6. the fan of d&b is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
 8. the brazilian is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
10. the mexican is in an even position##4
11. the mexican is on the far right##1
12. the fan of disco is on the right of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b      | disco | r&b     | country        |
| Nationality   | malaysian | brazilian  | indian     | mexican |
| Sport         | basketball    | soccer | biathlon      | skiing |
| Transport     | trike | airplane     | roller | taxi       |

 